he shorter height compensates for a thicker mattress height mattress foundations should have solid wood construction with diagonal bar corner supports and impact–protected plastic edges go the extra mile for comfort and treat yourself to a power base this holds an adjustable mattress perfect for personalizing your sleep position find a wide selection of power bases instore myashleyhome we love to see your style hashtag myashleyhome on instagram full gallery here bedding  ashley furniture homestore menu  furniturebackliving roombacksofas  couchesloveseatssectional sofas sleeper sofaspower seatingreclinerschairsottomanscoffee tableslifttop coffee tablesend  side tablesaccent tablessofa  console tablestv stands  mediastoragecreate your style your waybedroombackbedsheadboardsnightstandsdressersmirrored dresserschest of drawersbedroom chairsbenchesbeddingbed pillowsstoragehome officebackdesksoffice chairsbookcasesstorageentrywaykitchen  diningbackdining room tablesdining room setsdining room chairsbar stoolsbenchesdining room storagecollectionsbackporterzenfieldmarsilonamoretips  inspirationroom packagesbackbedroomdining roomliving roomhomestore specialsbackliving roombedroomdining roomhome officekids furnitureentertainmentsmall spacessave up to  on s of itemsshop all furnitureoutdoorbackpatio furniturebackseatingtableshammockslounge chairsoutdoor diningbackdining chairsdining tablespolywoodpatio accessoriesbackpatio umbrellasheatersfire pits  tablespillows  cushionshammock standsoutdoor setsbackdining setschat setspatio setssofa setsup to  off outdoorshop all outdoorkidsbackkids furniturebackbedsnightstandsbunk bedsdresserschest of drawersstorageboys furnituregirls furniturekids beddingbackbeddingcomfortersquiltsthrow pillowslightingrugswall decorsave up to  on s of itemsshop all kidshome decorbackhome accentsbackcandles  candle holderscanisters  jarsvases  bottlessculpturesbaskets  boxesbowls  trayspicture framesstorage  organizationdining  entertainingbackdinnerwaredr