d technology seal from nasa this seal verifies that the underlying product technology was derived from the united states efforts and experiments in space q where is tempur sealy® international inc stock traded a   tempur sealy international inc’s stock is traded on the new york stock exchange nyse under the ticker symbol tpx q when did tempur sealy® international inc become a public company a   the company became a publiclytraded company on december   q who is the stock transfer agent a   tempur sealy international incs stock transfer agent is american stock transfer  trust company llc more information is available at httpwwwamstockcommain q does tempur sealy® international inc pay cash dividends have a dividend reinvestment program or have a direct stock purchase plan a   tempur sealy international inc does not currently pay a dividend the company does not have a dividend reinvestment program or a direct purchase plan at this time q how can i buy tempur sealy® international inc stock a   you can purchase tempur sealy international inc common stock through any brokerage account our stock trades on the new york stock exchange under the ticker symbol tpx q has tempur sealy® international inc had any stock splits a   the company has not had any stock splits since becoming a publiclytraded company in december  q who is tempur sealy® international incs independent auditor a   the companys independent auditor is ernst and young llp q do you have another question that hasnt been answered please submit your question using the form below  required fields name    email    subject    comments    type in number    this helps tempur sealy international inc prevent automated submissions javascript is not enabled with javascript enabled this page will display content dynamically investor resources investor contacts email alerts request information shareholder briefcase investor faq investment calculator dividend history open  high  last  change   volume   min delay   tempurpedic m