tly transitioning away from oracle to microsoft dynamics for its erp solutions the it budget is typically finalized in q it intelligence snippets  •tempurpedic and sealy corporation recently merged to form tempur sealy international •migrated its email to microsoft office from lotus notes •implemented new voip solution in its north carolina office  •expecting it storage spending to increase in the areas of data protection and recovery software storage replication software archiving software storage related cloud initiatives and bigdata initiatives  •tempur sealy international inc describes oracle as its biggest storage headache its top storage pain points are wan being too slow wan optimization being too expensive and the lack of modernizingvirtualizing solutions for systems and tape that are no longer viable  •tempur sealy international inc uses disk backup across sandas environment to back up its block data  •it uses veritas netbackup with one master and media server as its main backup application its daily and weekly total data backup is tbtb and tb respectively with a  hour backup window its backup growth is around gb  •relating to its remote locations data is backed up locally and all remote locations have wan optimization deployed sector industry consumer goods consumer products manufacturers employees  revenue b fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  staffing topic finance staffing company tempur sealy international inc lexington ky opportunity seeking a staff accountant ar nc trinity  staffing topic finance staffing company tempur sealy international inc lexington ky opportunity seeking an assoc manager payroll nc trinity  staffing topic customer marketing staffing company tempur sealy international inc lexington ky opportunity seeking a customer marketing manager lexington ky  want full access to this profile and more rainkings clients have access to over  new investment signals published daily which provide insights on spending in